text: Charlie Chan at Treasure Island is a 1939 American crime movie directed by Norman Foster and starring Sidney Toler, Victor Sen Yung, Cesar Romero, Douglas Fowley, Pauline Moore, Donald MacBride, Wally Vernon, Billie Seward, Sally Byrne. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * Category:1939 crime movies Category:American crime movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Norman Foster Category:Movies set in San Francisco Category:Movies set in the 1930s Category:Charlie Chan
